Dialogue: 0,0:00:03.90,0:00:07.82,Main,G-Cis,0,0,0,,How long have I awaited this?{JP:長かったぞ！=It's been such a long time!}{EN:I've been waiting so long for this!}
Dialogue: 0,0:00:08.53,0:00:12.24,Main,G-Cis,0,0,0,,I’ve kept my silence, \N so no one could learn my plans.{EN:I've kept my silence so no one could piece together what I planned.}{JP:計画を　悟られぬよう息を　潜めていた……}
Dialogue: 0,0:00:12.99,0:00:16.50,Main,G-Cis,0,0,0,,{\fad(0, 1482)}The truth is this...
Dialogue: 0,0:00:18.08,0:00:24.25,Main,G-Cis,0,0,0,,I was unable to become a hero \N and acquire a Legendary Pokémon.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:25.30,0:00:28.63,Main,G-Cis,0,0,0,,So, I prepared someone \N for that purpose.{JP:ゲーチス『……ふはは！븁英雄に　なれぬ　ワタクシが伝説のポケモンを　手にする……븁そのためだけに　用意したのがその　Ｎ！！븁いってみれば　人の　心を　持たぬバケモノ　です븁そんな　いびつで　不完全な　人間に話が　通じると　思うのですか븁}{EN:Since I couldn't become the hero and obtain the legendary Pokémon myself... I prepared someone for that purpose--N! He's nothing more than a freak without a human heart. Do you think you're going to get through to a warped person like that?!}
Dialogue: 0,0:00:28.63,0:00:29.97,Main,N,0,0,0,,Look, over there!
Dialogue: 0,0:00:29.97,0:00:30.80,Main,N,0,0,0,,I won’t forget!{wasurenai kara sa!}
Dialogue: 0,0:00:30.80,0:00:33.22,Main,G-Cis,0,0,0,,A warped boy...
Dialogue: 0,0:00:33.22,0:00:35.77,Main,G-Cis,0,0,0,,...who knew of nothing \N but Pokémon.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:58.96,0:01:01.92,Main,G-Cis,0,0,0,,Ever since that moment,
Dialogue: 0,0:01:01.92,0:01:07.67,Main,G-Cis,0,0,0,,I’ve provided him with everything. \N Everything he needed to become a legendary hero...
Dialogue: 0,0:01:07.67,0:01:12.18,Main,G-Cis,0,0,0,,{\fad(0, 2023)}...and king of Team Plasma.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:52.43,0:01:57.64,Main,G-Cis,0,0,0,,I spurred N \N into pursuing ideals.{JP:ワタクシが Ｎに　理想を　追い求めさせ}{EN:I spurred N into pursuing ideals}
Dialogue: 0,0:01:58.43,0:02:04.27,Main,G-Cis,0,0,0,,If I could kindle within him \N the desire to make the world a better place,{JP:しかも　世界を　良くしたいという 熱い思いを　胸に　秘めている！}{EN:Added to all that, his heart burns with the desire to improve the world.}
Dialogue: 0,0:02:04.27,0:02:08.52,Main,G-Cis,0,0,0,,I knew we would surely \N seize the hearts of people.{JP:ここまで　舞台装置が　整えば 人々の　心は　つかめる！}{EN:Now that the stage is set, we can seize people's minds and hearts.}
Dialogue: 0,0:02:11.57,0:02:14.20,Main,Human being,0,0,0,,Looks like something’s \N about to happen in the plaza.{EN:Sounds like something's going on in the plaza!}{JP:なんか　広場で 始まるらしいぞ！}
Dialogue: 0,0:02:14.20,0:02:16.07,Main,Human being,0,0,0,,Well, should we take a peek?{JP:んじゃ　ちょいと 行ってみるかね}{EN:Well, let's have a little look-see.}
Dialogue: 0,0:02:18.03,0:02:19.20,Main,Touko,0,0,0,,Up you go.{Upsy-daisy.}
Dialogue: 0,0:02:40.06,0:02:43.52,Main,G-Cis,0,0,0,,Thank you \N for gathering here today.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:43.52,0:02:48.94,Main,G-Cis,0,0,0,,I am here today \N to talk to you about Pokémon liberation.{JP:今日　みなさんに　お話しするのはポケモン解放について　です}{EN:Today, ladies and gentlemen, I would like to talk to you about Pokémon liberation.}
Dialogue: 0,0:02:50.07,0:02:55.95,Main,G-Cis,0,0,0,,There is so much \N we can learn from Pokémon.{JP:われわれが　学ぶべき　ところを数多く　持つ　存在なのです}{EN:They are living beings from whom we humans have much to learn.}
Dialogue: 0,0:02:55.95,0:03:04.46,Main,G-Cis,0,0,0,,All of you listening, what should we \N be doing for these wonderful Pokemon?{JP:そんな　ポケモンたちに対し ワタクシたち　人間が すべきことは　なんでしょうか}{EN:Tell me, what is our responsibility toward these wonderful beings called Pokémon?}
Dialogue: 0,0:03:05.21,0:03:09.04,Main,G-Cis,0,0,0,,That’s right! \N We must liberate the Pokémon!{JP:そうです！ポケモンを　解放することです！！}{EN:That's right! We must liberate the Pokémon!}
Dialogue: 0,0:03:09.04,0:03:14.59,Main,G-Cis,0,0,0,,Then, for the first time in history, \N humans and Pokémon can become equals!{JP:そうしてこそ人間と　ポケモンは븀はじめて　対等になれるのです}{EN:Then, and only then, will humans and Pokémon truly be equals.} {Is "in history" too loose? I guess it could contradict a potential time where humans and Pokémon existed as complete separates. - Toa}{Well, the whole thing seems like an allegory for slavery given the US base of Isshu... So it kinda fits? -blu}
Dialogue: 0,0:03:32.40,0:03:35.28,Main,G-Cis,0,0,0,,I tested him...
Dialogue: 0,0:03:35.28,0:03:40.91,Main,G-Cis,0,0,0,,To find out if he could become a hero \N capable of reviving a legendary Pokémon.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:23.87,0:04:30.08,Main,G-Cis,0,0,0,,N demonstrated \N he was worthy of bearing my name.{JP:それでも　ワタクシと 同じ　ハルモニアの　名前をもつ 人間なのか？}{EN:After all of that, do you think you're still worthy of sharing the name Harmonia with me?}
Dialogue: 0,0:04:31.13,0:04:33.63,Main,G-Cis,0,0,0,,I even procured a castle \N fit for a king.{JP:王に　ふさわしい　城も すでに　用意して　いるのですよ}{EN:For this, we have prepared a suitable castle for the legendary Zekrom and our king!}
Dialogue: 0,0:04:34.09,0:04:37.05,Main,G-Cis,0,0,0,,A castle that can engulf \N and shroud the Pokémon League.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:37.05,0:04:40.59,Main,G-Cis,0,0,0,,A symbol showing \N that Isshu will change!{JP:ポケモンリーグを　包み隠すように出現した　城は イッシュが　変わることを 意味する　シンボル븁}{EN:The castle that appeared as if it were enveloping the Pokémon League is a symbol. It means Unova will change.}
Dialogue: 0,0:04:47.93,0:04:49.85,Main,Adeku,0,0,0,,Go! Ulgamoth!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:07.54,0:05:09.16,Main,Adeku,0,0,0,,G-Cis is a liar!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:09.62,0:05:13.79,Main,Adeku,0,0,0,,Your “liberation” \N is just stealing Pokémon from people!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:14.17,0:05:17.63,Main,Adeku,0,0,0,,He’s tricked you! \N He’s tricked everyone!{EN:Ghetsis... What a liar.븁Desperately trying to con everyone with his speech.}{JP:ウソつき　ゲーチスめ븁みなを　たぶらかそうと}
Dialogue: 0,0:05:33.02,0:05:37.48,Main,G-Cis,0,0,0,,Now, the strongest trainer, \N commanding a legendary Pokemon...
Dialogue: 0,0:05:37.48,0:05:39.90,Main,G-Cis,0,0,0,,...has fought the champion...
Dialogue: 0,0:05:39.90,0:05:41.95,Main,G-Cis,0,0,0,,and won!{JP:その城の　王は伝説の　ポケモンを　従え븀チャンピオンを　超えた븀最強の　トレーナー！븁しかも　世界を　良くしたいという熱い思いを　胸に　秘めている！}{EN:The king of this castle is the strongest Trainer in the world. He is accompanied by the legendary Pokémon. He has defeated the Champion.}
Dialogue: 0,0:05:43.32,0:05:44.57,Main,Adeku,0,0,0,,I beg you...
Dialogue: 0,0:05:44.57,0:05:48.20,Main,Adeku,0,0,0,,Please don’t separate \N people from Pokémon!{JP:頼む！ ポケモンと　人を　切り離す……それだけは　しないでくれっ！！}{EN:I beg you! Separating people from Pokémon... Do anything but that!}
Dialogue: 0,0:05:50.37,0:05:52.96,Main,G-Cis,0,0,0,,If you would not \N call him a hero,
Dialogue: 0,0:05:54.08,0:05:57.04,Main,G-Cis,0,0,0,,who could you ever \N call a hero?{JP:これを　英雄と　呼ばずして だれを　英雄と　呼ぶのです？}{EN:If that's not what makes a hero, what more do you need?}
Dialogue: 0,0:05:58.46,0:06:02.38,Main,Verbena,0,0,0,,Forget about destiny, \N and follow your heart.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:02.38,0:06:05.22,Main,Verbena,0,0,0,,Your heart is \N pure and innocent.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:05.22,0:06:08.97,Main,Helena,0,0,0,,But there’s nothing more beautiful \N and terrifying than innocence.{JP:あまりにも　ピュアでイノセントな　Ｎの　心…… イノセントほど美しく　怖いものは　ないのに}{EN:N's heart is pure and innocent. But there is nothing more beautiful and terrifying than innocence.}
Dialogue: 0,0:06:14.19,0:06:15.44,Main,G-Cis,0,0,0,,It’s time.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:16.81,0:06:18.27,Main,G-Cis,0,0,0,,Yes...
Dialogue: 0,0:06:18.27,0:06:21.40,Main,G-Cis,0,0,0,,How long have I awaited this?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:21.40,0:06:24.61,Main,G-Cis,0,0,0,,Now, those painful days are at an end!{JP:苦しみの　日々も　終わる！！븁}{EN:Now, those painful days are at an end!}
Dialogue: 0,0:06:24.61,0:06:29.37,Main,G-Cis,0,0,0,,My perfect plan \N is about to come to fruition.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:30.24,0:06:33.79,Main,G-Cis,0,0,0,,So that I may \N take control of the world,
Dialogue: 0,0:06:33.79,0:06:40.13,Main,G-Cis,0,0,0,,Team Plasma will steal everyone’s Pokemon \N and release them, “liberate” them!{JP:プラズマ団が\すべての　ポケモンを　人から븀奪い　逃がし　解き放ちましょう！}{EN:Team Plasma will steal every Pokémon from every person in the world and release them all!}
Dialogue: 0,0:06:44.22,0:06:45.43,Main,G-Cis,0,0,0,,Oh!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:45.43,0:06:48.30,Main,G-Cis,0,0,0,,So you’ve acquired \N the Light Stone.{JP:ライトストーンを　手にしたようですね}{EN:It seems that you have obtained the Light Stone.}
Dialogue: 0,0:06:49.97,0:06:53.81,Main,G-Cis,0,0,0,,If you truly desire to prolong a world \N where you can live alongside Pokémon,{JP:アナタが　このまま ポケモンと　共存する 世界を　望むのなら [...] われらの　王と　戦いなさい}{EN:If you truly desire to keep the world as it is, where Pokémon live alongside people, [...] battle with our king.}
Dialogue: 0,0:06:53.81,0:06:56.44,Main,G-Cis,0,0,0,,do battle with our king.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:56.44,0:06:58.27,Main,G-Cis,0,0,0,,Now, go onward!{JP:さあ　進め！}{EN:Go, onward!}
Dialogue: 0,0:06:58.27,0:07:03.19,Main,G-Cis,0,0,0,,Discover whether or not \N you can become a hero!{JP:そして　自分にも英雄の　資質が　あるか븀確かめれば　いいのです！}{EN:Discover whether you have what it takes to be a hero!}
Dialogue: 0,0:07:32.52,0:07:33.18,Main,N,0,0,0,,Come here,
Dialogue: 0,0:07:33.81,0:07:34.56,Main,N,0,0,0,,Zekrom!{JP:おいで　ゼクロム！}{EN:Zekrom! Come to me!}
Dialogue: 0,0:08:03.21,0:08:06.13,Main,G-Cis,0,0,0,,I will not allow anyone \N to stop me.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:06.88,0:08:09.89,Main,G-Cis,0,0,0,,No matter \N what they may try.{JP:だれが　なにを　しようと！ワタクシを　とめることは　できない！}{EN:I won't allow anyone to stop me! No matter who does what!}
Dialogue: 0,0:08:10.64,0:08:14.81,Main,G-Cis,0,0,0,,The world belongs to me!{EN:The world should be mine!}{JP:doesn't exist}
